sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant UsersAPI
    participant PostgreSQL
    participant RabbitMQ
    participant NotificationAPI
    participant SMTP

    Client->>UsersAPI: POST /api/auth/register
    UsersAPI->>PostgreSQL: Create User
    PostgreSQL-->>UsersAPI: User created
    UsersAPI->>RabbitMQ: Publish UserRegisteredEvent
    UsersAPI-->>Client: 200 OK (AuthResult)

    RabbitMQ->>NotificationAPI: Deliver Event
    NotificationAPI->>NotificationAPI: Select Strategy
    NotificationAPI->>SMTP: Send Welcome Email
    SMTP-->>NotificationAPI: Email sent